# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# packages/devbox/.secrets.example — Story 2.2 (AC 4)
#
# Committed schema for the `act` local GitHub-Actions runner. Forks copy
# this file to `packages/devbox/.secrets` (gitignored per Story 2.2 AC 5)
# and populate with per-fork dev values before invoking `act`.
#
# Source of truth for the key set: architecture.md:328-330 § I6.
# Production / CI secret source: GitHub repo → Settings → Secrets and
# variables → Actions. `.secrets` mirrors those keys locally so the act
# runner can exercise GH Actions workflows without cloud credentials.
# CI tier scoping: pre-merge-slow / nightly / release-gated only — the
# pre-merge-fast tier runs with ZERO external secrets per architecture.md:329.
#
# Format: one-line `<KEY>=<value>` — no quotes, no leading whitespace per
# act's parser. Copy-seed flow: `cp packages/devbox/.secrets.example
# packages/devbox/.secrets` and fill in per-fork values. See
# packages/devbox/README.md § Retuning § Secrets for the consumer flow.
# Future consumer: .github/workflows/*.yml (Epic 13).
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# --- Billing (Paddle; Epic 10) ---
PADDLE_SANDBOX_API_KEY=
PADDLE_PROD_API_KEY=

# --- Email (Resend; Epic 8) ---
RESEND_API_KEY=

# --- OAuth (Google; Epic 9) ---
GOOGLE_OAUTH_CLIENT_SECRET=

# --- Anthropic (Tier-2 deviation path; see PRD NFR28b honesty posture) ---
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# --- Database (ephemeral Postgres DSN; pre-merge-slow CI tier — Epic 13) ---
DATABASE_URL_EPHEMERAL=
